Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我從來沒有給新長官支付過這麼多{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And that's more than I've ever paid any first officer.{\r}
