Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}下次你就會是船長{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}next time you WILL have your captaincy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你之前給過我保證來 馬森先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You've given me your word before, Mr. Mason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這次我需要書面保證{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}So, this time I'll take it in writing.{\r}
