Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我很高興聽到{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I'm glad to hear it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}現在我得照顧個沒經驗的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Now I'm to babysit a greenhorn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一個含著他媽的金勺長大的船長了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Some cheerless Nantucket born with a damned silver spoon in his mouth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我真應該當面拒絕{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I should have thrown their offer back in their faces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}為什麼 你已經拿到書面承諾了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Why? You now have the offer of command in writing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}騙子的世界什麼都是假的 即使是書面承諾{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Yes, well, a liar's word is worthless, even ON paper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你知道即使你是商人我還是會愛上你的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You know I'd love you just as much if you were a merchant captain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你不能離開兩年之久{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And you wouldn't be gone for two years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我不會離開兩年之久的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I won't be gone two years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}貝德福德家的捕鯨人上周回來了 離開了有三年{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}A Bedford whaler came back last week was gone three.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}她失去了兩個男人 而且驚魂落魄{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}She lost two men and still with her hull half empty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們是貝德福德家 沒有我在{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, they were from Bedford and they didn't have me aboard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}婊子養的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Son of a bitch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我要指揮我自己的船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I will captain my own ship...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一艘捕鯨船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}a whaling ship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}靠他們我們只能永遠在這個鬼地方{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Up to them all we'd ever have is a patch of dirt{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我不會讓這發生的 佩吉{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}and that's not going to happen, Peggy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你父親也是這麼說的 你不能這麼說{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Those'd be your father's words, not yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他的話怎麼了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}What's wrong with his words?{\r}
