Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}夢想大海 不帶那些廢物們出海{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Dreamed of the sea and never got to sea with men like them.{\r}
