Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}對不起{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我嫁給了一個捕鯨人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I married a whaleman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我會盡快回來 我發誓{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I'll come back as quick as the sun is night, I swear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一定要回來 向我保證{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Please come back... promise me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我已經向你發誓了 你還要我保證{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I already swore to you, now you want me to promise, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我保證{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I promise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}孩子 跟你說句話{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Son, a word with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}當船長 你不能當他們的朋友 你是他們的長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}To be a captain, you cannot be a friend, you are their superior.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}別忘了這點 讓別人記住這點{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Never forget that, never let THEM forget that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}謝謝{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Thank you, son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你的曾祖父和其他人創立了這個行業{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Your great-grandfather and a few others created this industry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}沒有我們 沒有你們 世界將會陷入黑暗{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Without us, without you, the world plunges into darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我希望能讓家族名譽生輝 先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I hope to bring honor to the Pollard family name, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}啊 上帝創造了巨大的鯨 體長無比的神奇怪物{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Thou didst, O Lord, create the mighty whale, That wondrous monster of a mighty length;{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}頭碩身龐尾又闊 無邊雄力人難度{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Beyond conception his unmeasured strength.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}恆古上帝宥永生 吾儕荏弱落凡塵{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}But, everlasting God, thou dost ordain that we, poor feeble mortals{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}妻兒一家須偷生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}should engage ourselves, our wives and children to maintain,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}賴此巨物維生存{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}This dreadful monster with a martial rage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}啊 上帝 用您的榮耀之光照亮這些男人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}O Father, grant that your glorious light shine on these men,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}保佑他們豐收的航程{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}and assure them a prosperous voyage,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}保佑他們安全歸來{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}that they may return SAFELY unto the womb ship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}楠塔基特的白鯨油{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}So that the white whales of Nantucket whale oil{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}可以繼續照亮我們的房屋{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}may continue to keep light in our homes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}照亮我們的街道 為工業機器提供燃料{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}city streets safe from sin in the night, fuel the machines of industry,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}推動我們偉大的國家前進{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}drive our great nation forward,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們文明種族進步 我們祈禱{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}as our noble species evolves. In Your name, we pray.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}現在是幾月{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}So, what month is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}年末了 我們是最後一批出海的船隻了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Oh, late in the year, we were one of the last ships to go out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}也是為什麼我和我朋友巴爾齊萊有臥鋪{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Which is why my friend Barzillai and I got a berth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}聽著 我當時14歲{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Look, I was fourteen... fourteen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}尼克森 別站著 幹活{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Nickerson, you're standin' around, boy! Move!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}第一次出海 很害怕 更害怕顯露出來{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}First time at sea, scared, more scared to show it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}巴爾齊萊當時17歲{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Barzillai was seventeen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}在碼頭長大的孤兒都等不及被別人視作大人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Orphans, grew up on the wharf, both in a hurry to be called men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你們慢騰騰幹嘛 裝船 快 快{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}What are you all guys waiting for? Get it aboard! C'mon! Haul away...!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們戴的是飾針是什麼{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}What are those pins they're wearing?{\r}
