Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我怎麼才能得到一個{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}How do I get one of them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你得用長矛刺殺一頭白鯨{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, you've gotta thrust a killing lance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}那是世界上最大的怪物{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The largest beast ever to breathe on the earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}尼克森 把那綠色的東西給邦德先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Nickerson, get the green stuff to Mr. Bond.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}快點 媽的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Make it quick, damn it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我總有一天會有一堆那東西{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I shall have twelve of those one day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}把它們放到匣子喎\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Put 'em on the Grandira casket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你也上船就說明一件事{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, well, you being on board means only one thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}是啊 這船上至少有一人明白歐文·查斯是誰{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Yep! At least there's one person on this ship who knows the truth about Owen Chase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不 可惜其他的船都已經滿員了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}No, but all the other ships have already crewed up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不不 我洗心革面了 歐文 問題是你呢{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}No, no, I'm a reformed man, Owen, the question is are YOU?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}別告訴我花花公子馬修戒酒了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Don't tell me Matthew Joy has put down the bottle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我有罪 歐文·查斯能消消他的壞脾氣了嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I have sinned. Has Owen Chase put down his temper?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}平靜的像教堂{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Serene as the Church.{\r}
