Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}考慮到我們的船長 我覺得你只能平靜一小會兒{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Given our captain I'll give your serenity about 48 hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}祝你好運{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Good luck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}波拉德 喬治·波拉德 歐文·查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Pollard, George Pollard. - Owen Chase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯 你父親的名字對嗎 對 是的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Chase, your father's name, isn't it? - Yes, it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}馬上他要離開島一段時間而我舒適得待在家{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Very shortly he will be off island for some time and I'll be very much at home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我要說 我有點意外 通常船長可以選擇自己的大副{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I say, I was surprised, normally a captain gets to choose his first mate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果是有經驗的船長的話 是的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}An experienced captain, yes.{\r}
