Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}確實{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Indeed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們也許想要多些保障{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They probably wanted a little extra reassurance, that's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}看著點我 如果我做錯什麼了告訴我{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, DO keep an eye on me, let me know if I'm doing anything wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我不會遲疑的 船長{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I'd have it not other way, Captain.{\r}
