Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}起風了 頂部橫桿放下了嗎 好{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Head's in the wind, is the top rail off? - Aye.{\r}
