Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}科爾 查普爾 守在起錨器旁{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Cole, Mr. Chappel, stand by this anchor!{\r}
