Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}為什麼帆布還沒有鬆開{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Boyd! Why aren't those braces laid out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}打開帆 媽的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Set the sail, god damn it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}跑開{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Heading to scram.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}船長 注意頭上 後面 船長{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Captain! Heads up! - Behind you head, Captain!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}怎麼了 謝潑德 帆布纏住了 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- What happened, Mr. Sheppard? - The jalousie felled the sheet, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}帆布纏住了 查斯 他辦不到{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- The jalousie's jammed! - Chase, she still won't clear!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}當心{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Watch your step!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}帆布 歐文{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It's the jalousie, Owen!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}走開{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Stand clear!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}幹的漂亮 查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Nice piece of work, Mr. Chase!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果兩周內能到佛得角{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}If we make Cape Verdes in the next 2 weeks we'll{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們有很大幾率能按時到太平洋{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}have a decent chance of reaching the Pacific on schedule.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}玉米棒 查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Corn, Mr. Chase?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不需要 謝謝 從來不喜歡{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}No, thank you, Sir, never did have much of a taste for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}太怪了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That's odd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你爸在科德角是種玉米的吧 是的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- So, your father grew corn on Cape Cod. - That's right, he did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你也猜到了 我那時天天吃這個吃膩了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}As you can imagine, I suddenly grew tired of eating it every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}種玉米 秋葵 大豆 然後他進了監獄{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Corn, okra, beans, I believe? Before he went to jail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}花花公子 聽起來熟悉嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Are you familiar with this story, Mr. Joy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你知道查斯是因為他的父親進監獄才變成孤兒的嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Were you aware that Mr. Chase was effectively orphaned due to his father's incarceration?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們都有不同的經歷{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, we all have our paths to sea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}所以還是不要問太多問題為好{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That's a motive to not ask too many questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一定不容易吧{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Can't have been easy though, yet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}楠塔基特最偉大的航海家族收留你{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You had Nantucket's great seafaring family to adopt you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}很久沒有楠塔基特人稱呼我陸人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}This is far from the first time I've been called a landsman...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}或者提醒我不是他們一家人了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}or off-islander by some Nantucket reminding me how I am NOT part of their family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}請允許我 船長 我要去分配捕鯨船和值班了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Now, if the captain will excuse me, there are whale boats and watches to assign.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不 船長 滴酒不沾{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- No, Sir, not for me. - Not a drop?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不 船長 就像我說的 有時候少問問題更好{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}No, Sir, like I said, sometimes the fewer questions one asks, the better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}花花公子 這有個漂亮姑娘{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That's a gorgeous girl, Mr. Joy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}遠東的鯨骨上刻的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Region of move me that, carved from a Far East whalebone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不許碰{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}No touching!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我一直以為你已經結婚了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I always thought you were married anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}是的 但看她{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I am, and there she is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這是她的鼻子{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, that's her nose anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}恭喜 女士們{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Congratulations, ladies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}今天啟航幹的不錯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That was a fine job trimin' sails today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我從來沒有過這麼一群捕鯨人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}A sorrier pack of deck-whalers I don't think I've ever seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查普爾 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Mr. Chappel. - Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}船長魚叉手{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Captain's harpooner.{\r}
