Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}彼得森 二副的魚叉手{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And Mr. Peterson, second mate's harpooner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}遵命 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Aye, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一船上六人 首要一點要警覺{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}There'll be six men to a boat, first rules in the row, six bells sharp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們還沒到哈利法克斯以東 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We're not even east of Halifax, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你叫什麼 克芬 亨利·克芬{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- What's your name? - Coffin, Henry Coffin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他是船長的表弟 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}He's the Captain's cousin, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}克芬先生 你覺得一頭白鯨會知道自己在哈利法克斯以東嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, well, Mr. Coffin, do you think a whale knows it's east of Halifax?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我不知道你們原來是誰 或者怎麼來的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I don't know who all of you are, or how you got here,{\r}
