Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}沒關係 我不關心 我對你們的要求只有一個{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That's fine, I don't give a damn, but we interred you for just one thing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.95,0:24:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}只有一個 就是鯨油{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}and one thing only, and that is whale oil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我要裝滿2000桶油並盡快回家{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I intend to fill our 2000 barrels and be home as quickly as possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}即使天氣好而且沒有鯨出沒 克芬先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And even when the weather is fine and there ARE no whales, Mr. Coffin,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們會放下船練習如何捕鯨{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}we will lower the boats and practice all maneuvers necessary in a capture of a whale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}誰要是想偷懶就自己游回家 明白嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And any man who is idle will find himself swimmin' to home. Is that understood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}明白 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Aye, sir. Aye, Sir. - Aye, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}小子 上甲板{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Green horn, on deck!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.94,0:25:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}走{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}On ya go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}遵命 遵命 陸人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Aye, aye, landsman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.51,0:25:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}湯姆·尼克森 對吧 是的 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Thomas Nickerson, right? - Aye, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.15,0:25:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}有些人一開始會覺得噁心{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Ya know, some feel sick at first.{\r}
