Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.56,0:26:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你離學會捕鯨和航行還差遠了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You're a long way from base to be whaling and sailing.{\r}
