Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.72,0:26:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果有必要我們會訓練到日落{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We'll stay at this until sunlight if we have to.{\r}
