Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.56,0:26:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}魚叉手準備乘船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Harpooners make ready to boat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.79,0:26:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}雷 動作快點 我的錯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Need to move quicker, Mr. Ray! - My mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}沒有女人玩了 查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Ain't no more wee whores, Mr. Chase.{\r}
