Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.91,0:27:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}幹的不錯 雷{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Not bad, Mr. Ray, well done!{\r}
