Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.33,0:27:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Mr. Chase. - Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.78,0:27:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}揚帆{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Set stuns'ls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.21,0:27:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這樣做好嗎 長官 我們接近洋流{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Is that wise, Sir, we're near the Gulf Stream.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.12,0:27:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}看這天氣也還得緩慢前進{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Best to be five knots fto even see the weather.{\r}
