Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.50,0:27:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你得在東風來臨前彌補上時間{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You need to make up the time before we catch the east wind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.53,0:27:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}揚帆{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Set stuns'ls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.69,0:27:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}揚帆{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Set stuns'ls.{\r}
