Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}克芬 鬆開帆 船長要提速{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Get her off, Mr. Coffin, the Captain wants speed!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}遵命 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Aye, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}她老了 但是還能讓我們爽 哈哈{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}She might be old but she can still blow, boys!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}長官 右舷方向有一颶風團 我們需要馬上降帆{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Sir, a squall on the starboard route, we need to shorten the sail immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.11,0:28:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}還不行 查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Not just yet, Mr. Chase.{\r}
