Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.79,1:21:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}什麼船長{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Captain of what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.96,1:21:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}埃塞克斯號沉沒了不是你的責任{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The Essex was lost and no fault o'yours.{\r}
