Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.85,1:22:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你天生就是幹這活的料{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You were born to do this job.{\r}
