Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.83,1:22:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們幹了什麼 你覺得 喬治{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}What we do, do ya think, George?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.46,1:22:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們幹了什麼冒犯了上帝 讓他這麼不開心{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}What offense did we give God to upset him so?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.58,1:22:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}冒犯上帝的是那些白鯨{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The only creature to have offended God here is the whale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.28,1:22:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不是我們{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Not us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.38,1:22:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不是我們的傲慢 我們的貪婪 看我們現在在哪兒{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Not our arrogance, our greed? Look where we find ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.05,1:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們是上帝按自己喜好創造出來的高級生物{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We are supreme creatures made in God's own likeness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.98,1:22:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們是地球上的主宰{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We're earthly kings,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.86,1:22:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們要環航我們居住的星球{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}whose business it is to circumnavigate the planet bestowed to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.25,1:22:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}將自然屈服於我們的意志{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And to bend nature to OUR will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.52,1:23:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們經歷了這麼多你還覺得主宰一切嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You really feel like an earthly king after everything that we've been through?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.56,1:23:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們什麼都不是 我們是微粒 灰塵 但是我們{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- We're nothing... we're specks... dust. - But we're...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.07,1:23:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}拂曉時朝太陽方向行駛{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We sail into the sun at dawn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.49,1:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果我們要死 死在上帝的光輝喎\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}If we are to die, with God's grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.13,1:23:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}讓我們像男人一樣死去{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Let us die as men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.44,1:23:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們準備好了嗎 維克斯先生 是的 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Are we ready, Mr. Weeks? - Aye, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.57,1:23:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查普爾先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chappel.{\r}
