Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.11,1:23:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}準備出發 馬修{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Ready to go, Matthew?{\r}
