Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.23,1:30:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}聽著{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Listen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.64,1:30:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}媽的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Damn thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.08,1:30:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們還有些水{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We still got a few drops of the water left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.69,1:30:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}別放棄 我們要回家了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Don't ya quit on me, we're goin' home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.94,1:30:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你還有家人在嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Do you have a family...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.39,1:31:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}back home, Mr. Chase?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.26,1:31:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}有的 我的妻子{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Yeah, I have wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.49,1:31:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}對 還有一個兒子和一個女兒{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Yes, and a son or a daughter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.49,1:31:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}困住的第71天 南美以西1200海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.00,1:31:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}好{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Very well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.32,1:32:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}船長 我們重新抽籤{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Cap'n, we'll draw again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.29,1:32:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們不會這麼做{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We'll do no such thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.53,1:32:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們重新抽 拉姆斯德爾先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- We'll draw again. - Mr. Ramsdell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.29,1:32:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你要用這槍來指揮{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}you will assume command of this vessel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.96,1:32:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你明白{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Ya got that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.15,1:32:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你是我們的船長 你的船員需要你{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You're our cap'n, your men need you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.54,1:32:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}船員沒事的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The men will be fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.11,1:32:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}拜託了 拜託了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Please. Please. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.92,1:32:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}亨利 讓我們再抽籤{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Henry... - Let us go again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.52,1:32:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這是命令{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It is an order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.56,1:32:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果你做不到{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}If you cannot do it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.56,1:32:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}把槍給其他人{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}pass the pistol to another man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.89,1:33:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們在赤道無風帶幾周了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We were weeks in the Doldrums.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.32,1:33:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}太平洋那片區域遠比海洋枯竭{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That part of the Pacific is more desert than ocean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.80,1:33:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}太陽炙熱{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The sun beating down...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.74,1:33:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我害怕{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}My fear...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.20,1:33:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我能想到的是{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}All I could think about...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.69,1:33:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}所有人都會死而我是最後一個活著的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}was that everyone would die and I'd be the last left alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.68,1:33:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯只知道我們離陸地還有800英里{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Well, as best as Mr. Chase could tell, we were still 800 miles from land.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.94,1:33:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.44,1:34:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}船長波拉德{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Cap'n Pollard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.51,1:34:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}很高興見到你{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Very happy to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.04,1:34:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們生存下來沒什麼值得高興{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Very little happiness in our survival.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.23,1:34:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們也是 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Nor in ours, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.37,1:34:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}巴爾齊萊號{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Barzillai?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.61,1:34:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}另一艘船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The third boat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.21,1:34:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們不見了 幾天不見了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They're gone, they've been gone for days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.92,1:34:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我估計他們迷失了 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I'm afraid they're lost, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.00,1:35:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生 你為這個準備好了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chase, you are prepared for this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.90,1:35:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}不過是頭白鯨{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It's just a whale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.64,1:35:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}那 投茅{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}There! Throw the lance!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.56,1:35:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}投啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Throw it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.63,1:35:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}投啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Throw it, drown the lad!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.57,1:35:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}投啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Throw it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.09,1:36:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}就是現在 投茅啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Do it! Now! Throw the lance!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.44,1:36:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你為什麼不投{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Why didn't you throw it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.05,1:36:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你他媽是個傻子{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You're a damn fool.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.97,1:37:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}洋流把我們拆散了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}The current drew us apart...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.73,1:37:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}那是我們最後一次見到船長波拉德的鯨船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}and that was the last we would see of Captain Pollard's whale boat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.73,1:37:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}困住的第87天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.04,1:37:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}一艘船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}A boat!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.47,1:37:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}前方有一艘船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}A boat on the forward bow!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.09,1:37:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}上帝仁慈{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}May god have mercy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.09,1:38:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}困住的第90天 1821年2月18日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.57,1:38:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.28,1:38:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}父親{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Father...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.99,1:38:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}別丟下我 父親{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}don't leave me, Father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.19,1:39:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}嘿 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Hey, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.97,1:39:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生 長官 看 看 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chase. Sir. Look. Look, Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.94,1:39:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.79,1:39:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}看 那喎\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Look. Out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.38,1:39:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們來了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They're coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.74,1:40:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們來救我們了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They're coming for us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.03,1:40:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們在那堻Q救了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We were rescued there, off the Isle of MVs Afuera, Chile,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.92,1:40:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}埃塞克斯號沉船90天後{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}ninety days after the sinking of the Essex.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.33,1:40:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們給我們一些衣服和皮革吃{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They gave us some old clothes... leathers, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.31,1:40:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}起先感覺很難吃{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It was hard to eat at first... strange.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.34,1:40:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們盡力照顧我們{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They looked after us as best they could,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.23,1:40:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}然後他們找到了可以帶我們回家的一艘船{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}then we found a ship that could carry us home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.27,1:40:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}回家又花了三個月{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}That voyage took another three months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.27,1:40:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}1821年6月11日 楠塔基特港口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.63,1:41:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}全島的人好像都過來看我們回來{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It looked like the whole Island turned out to see us return.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.33,1:41:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}但是沒有歡呼 只有沉寂{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}But there were no cheers... only silence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.20,1:41:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他們看我們的樣子像是看到鬼 幽靈{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}They looked at us like we were... apparitions... phantoms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.74,1:41:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們沒有對任何人說起我們生存的細節{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}We'd said nothing of the details of our survival to anyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.06,1:41:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}但是我猜他們知道我們的困境{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}But I wondered if they somehow knew of our privations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.25,1:41:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}也許他們只是好奇{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Maybe they were just curious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.07,1:42:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我保證過的 不是嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}I promised, didn't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.51,1:42:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}天啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.89,1:42:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}嘿 寶貝 你是誰啊{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Hey, Sweetie! Who is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.08,1:42:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}菲比安{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Phebe Ann.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.03,1:42:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}菲比安·查斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Phebe Ann Chase.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.93,1:42:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他是你的父親{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It's your Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.35,1:42:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}嘿 寶貝{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Hey, Sweetie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.93,1:42:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他是你的父親{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It's your Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.20,1:43:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}當然還是有人找上他{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Of course they couldn't leave him alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.71,1:43:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}查斯先生和他的妻子往家走了不久{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Mr. Chase and his wife had scarcely walked a block towards home{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.73,1:43:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}他就被攔下來並帶回了海事辦公室{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}when he was stopped and made to return to the Maritime Office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.34,1:43:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}生意上的事還有疑問{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}There were business matters still in question.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.05,1:43:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}對於這件事{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}So, to the matter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.11,1:43:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}因為我們此次航線造成了巨大的人員和財產損失{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Due to the significant loss of life and property on our voyage,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.12,1:43:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}將會有一場聽證會{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}it seems there will be an inquiry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.07,1:43:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}作為船長和大副 我們需要交待事實經過{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And, as Captain and first mate, we will be expected to give account of what happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.96,1:43:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}是的 當然{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Yes, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.35,1:44:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我就這件事和船主和我父親討論過{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And, having discussed this with the ship owners and... my father,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.04,1:44:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}顯然完全交待經過會有後果{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}it is clear that full disclosure will have ramifications...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.27,1:44:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}對整個行業有可怕的後果{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}terrible ramifications for whole industry.{\r}
