Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.04,1:44:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}如果保險商和投資人開始擔心{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}If the insurance houses and investors were to start worrying about...{\r}
