Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.23,1:44:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}水手們很難活下來{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}sailors drawing lots to survive...{\r}
