Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.17,1:45:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}想想吧 他們會讓你當船長{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Think on it... they will make you captain.{\r}
