Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.74,1:45:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你要我為了功名掩蓋發生的一切{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}You want me to whitewash what happened for profit?{\r}
