Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.97,1:45:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們倖存下來的在裝備不良的捕鯨船上{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And those of us that survived in ill-equipped whale boats{\r}
