Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.20,1:45:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}我們回來後 又被指望傳播公然露骨的謊言{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}And on our return, we're expected to spread barefaced lies,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.70,1:46:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}好讓你們這些楠塔基特島島船主們{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}so that you, the ship owners of Nantucket,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.31,1:46:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}賺錢晚上再睡得安穩覺嗎{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}might line your pockets and sleep well at night?{\r}
