Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.03,1:47:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}祝你好運 湯姆斯{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Good luck out there, Thomas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.04,1:47:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}謝謝 長官{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Thank you, Sir.{\r}
