Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.33,1:49:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這二月的夜晚真是一年中最漫長的{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}These February nights are the longest of the year.{\r}
