Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.65,1:50:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}你得到了你的故事 情節都有了{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}Ya got your story there, and your plot is all there.{\r}
