Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.18,1:50:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}這會是部虛構的小說 尼克森先生{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}It will be a work of fiction, Mr. Nickerson,{\r}
