Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.33,1:51:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\bord1\shad0}謝謝 給{\r}\N{\fs12\bord1\shad0}- Thank you. - Here...{\r}
